summary: TRUMP claims that the United States should have private health care because Obamacare is a disaster and there is a lack of competition in the current system. This claim was made during the debate in Milwaukee, Wisconsin on April 1st, 216.
TRUMP claims during the debate in Milwaukee, Wisconsin on April 1st, 2016 that he doesn't want more nuclear weapons.

COOPER claims that a lot has changed since he asked Donald Trump if he would support the Republican nominee more than six months ago during a Republican Town Hall in Milwaukee, Wisconsin on April 1st, 216.
CLAIM: TRUMP claims that he did not mislead anyone and that the security cameras exonerate him during the debate in Milwaukee, Wisconsin on April 1st, 216.
